Subject to subsection (d) of this section, the Commission shall be comprised of:
One member from the Democratic Central Committee of Allegany County;
One member from the Republican Central Committee of Allegany County;
One member of the Allegany County Chamber of Commerce;
One member of the Allegany County Fire and Rescue Association;
One member of the Farm Bureau of Allegany County;
One member of the League of Women Voters of Allegany County; and
One member of the Western Maryland Central Labor Council.
